cff_report        ps_cff_report           pf_cff_report
STEP 2 — Get Partition Boundaries Dynamically
SQL
Copy code
SELECT
CAST(prv.value AS VARCHAR(50)) AS boundary_value
FROM sys.partition_functions pf
JOIN sys.partition_range_values prv
ON pf.function_id=prv.function_id
WHERE pf.name='pf_cff_report'
ORDER BY prv.boundary_id
